            <title><![CDATA[Stopped COVID again!]]></title>
            <link>https://itsairborne.com/stopped-covid-again-4cf2917e97ed?source=rss----ad92f7f89396--twitter_threads</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://medium.com/p/4cf2917e97ed</guid>
